line_1: Now, Memory, fail! nor let my mind revolve,
line_2: How England's Peers annull'd the just resolve,

line_1: Hence in dark heaps, ye gathering Clouds, revolve!
line_2: Disperse, ye Lightnings! and, ye Mists, dissolve!

line_1: Polite in Manners, and as Years Revolve;
line_2: Sedate in Thought, and steady in Resolve,
